{"tid":2335762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「2020 KBS歌謠大慶典」(G)I-DLE舒華搭檔IZ*ONE張員瑛頻繁出錯被罵：其實只排過一次走位而已","createTime":"2020-12-22T06:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T16:46:19.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c1defb786d1d978ce2ef8f62a8df12f502ed6dd9","tid":2335762,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"「2020 KBS 歌謠大慶典」上(G)I-DLE成員舒華舞蹈頻繁出錯，被不少觀眾吐槽。<br />\n<br />\n12月18日舉行的歌謠大慶典上（G）I-DLE的舒華和Oh My Girl Arin、IZ*ONE張員瑛和ITZY Yuna組成限定小分隊為觀眾們呈獻了特別舞台，重新演繹了APINK的《不知道》。 4人穿著夢幻色系的紗裙亮相，跳起來時裙擺飛揚，宛若花叢裡的精靈，十分唯美浪漫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e6eeb2e24df9b076532e747ef66db6a5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-22/132489-889962.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e6eeb2e24df9b076532e747ef66db6a5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-22%2F132489-889962.png&h=b6e2fb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本是一場視覺盛宴，但表演結束後不少觀眾就提出了意見，原因是舒華跳錯了好幾個動作，無法融入團隊的表演，大家留言稱：「太扎眼了，很明顯就和其他人不一樣」、「這是特別演出，竟然跳不整齊」等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/oJweB8Z7XJQV55tgvB/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FoJweB8Z7XJQV55tgvB%2Fgiphy.gif&h=4ddaff89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/Vy291d4LVVkrCuFyYl/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FVy291d4LVVkrCuFyYl%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b86952be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二天舒華就在個人直播里提到了這個事情，解釋稱最近（G）I-DLE工作太忙，自己和張員瑛等人只排過一次走位，接著就直接去錄製了。 舒華也很委屈，說道：「雖然沒有練習的時間，但我真的很努力。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ad4e7764819ad3aaa7c2569df9b2dc5a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-22/132489-889963.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ad4e7764819ad3aaa7c2569df9b2dc5a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-22%2F132489-889963.png&h=eefbde12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舒華的解釋並沒有得到網友的理解和認可，不少人覺得作為專業歌手，跳對動作是最基本的職業素養，且其他成員也都是同樣的練習時間，為什麼她們就沒有出錯。也有很多粉絲安慰舒華，希望她不要在意質疑聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xuH4YbWQBug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxuH4YbWQBug&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=702eb714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xuH4YbWQBug</a>"},{"pid":"2bcc666f221a3210e37b4aac6ddfba26c019d2d6","tid":2335762,"uid":229026,"like":21,"dislike":14,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"瑛妹很叻女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc1c505498db51b8e7937b3cefe86fa19067a02","tid":2335762,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa2f81ffd8d84a9262da59fa424ba5e30d2daee","tid":2335762,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":44,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:17:39.000Z","msg":"Arin快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa29e391f1b9807fb92fa934c1de669ea7ef7281","tid":2335762,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8cc1c505498db51b8e7937b3cefe86fa19067a02","tid":2335762,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T06:18:04.000Z","msg":"Gchi舒華?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32bfa9ba3aabef205225213ca7cca20d6fb8b91","tid":2335762,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fa2f81ffd8d8